get_game_list

Source: R/game_functions.R
get_game_list.Rd

This function fetches a basic list of games.

get_game_list(season = NULL)

Arguments

season

To retrieve prior season data, enter a 2-digit year corresponding to the start of the historical FPL season of interest (e.g. '18' for the 2018/2019 season).

Examples

get_game_list()
